-- Bharat Petroleum, Hindustan Petroleum Shares Rated New `Reduce' at BNP
-- Shiyin Chen
-- 2010-07-25T23:13:57Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/bharat-petroleum-hindustan-petroleum-shares-rated-new-reduce-at-bnp.html

          
          
             Bharat Petroleum Corp. and Hindustan
Petroleum Corp. were rated “reduce” in new coverage by BNP
Paribas analysts Amit Shah and Sriram Ramesh, who advised
investors to “look for a point to take profits.”  
 The analysts have a share-price estimate of 547 rupees for
Bharat Petroleum and a forecast of 366 rupees for Hindustan
Petroleum.  
 To contact the reporter on this story:
